    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for Model Risk Level 2. The six non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per the MRL 2 determination for a Class II device with Medium model influence. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions and comparison against the predicate device using the relative hemolysis index criterion (RH < 1). The assessment package is accepted as supporting the regulatory submission.",
